[14.849721, "o", "  The pickle scanner uses Python's pickletools to disassemble weight\r\n  files WITHOUT executing them. Any GLOBAL opcode referencing a\r\n  non-allowlisted module (os, subprocess, socket, requests, ...) is\r\n  flagged. The CycloneDX SBOM fragment integrates with Anchore /\r\n  Snyk / Trivy / Dependabot for downstream supply-chain tooling.\r\n"]
